WEBVTT

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:07.200
Brother Liang and Brother Chen are getting more and more impressive

00:01:07.920 --> 00:01:08.959
While I only know how to do the accounts

00:01:09.599 --> 00:01:11.040
I can't keep up with them anymore

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:12.560
If one day

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:14.159
they really close the club and the internet cafe

00:01:14.599 --> 00:01:16.000
then I'll be useless

00:01:20.079 --> 00:01:20.599
Bottoms up

00:01:22.959 --> 00:01:23.439
Wenjie

00:01:24.120 --> 00:01:25.239
Where are Chen Fan and Liang Shichu?

00:01:25.519 --> 00:01:26.319
Brother Hong Hai, you're here

00:01:26.760 --> 00:01:28.239
They went to meet the media

00:01:28.599 --> 00:01:29.680
They'll probably be back late

00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:30.760
Did you need them for something?

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:31.400
Just wanted to chat with them

00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:32.760
about that Mecha Shanghai game

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:34.439
Once this game got hot

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:36.079
a lot of people have been looking for them

00:01:36.359 --> 00:01:37.760
They're both crazy busy right now

00:01:45.319 --> 00:01:47.040
They went out to have fun without you again?

00:01:47.439 --> 00:01:49.079
Did they not invite you to the river last time either?

00:01:51.599 --> 00:01:52.159
No

00:01:52.640 --> 00:01:53.599
They are busy with serious business

00:01:53.760 --> 00:01:55.280
I'm just organizing things here

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:56.040
Come on

00:01:56.439 --> 00:01:57.760
Others might not know, but I do

00:01:58.079 --> 00:01:59.840
You've been partners with them for so long

00:01:59.959 --> 00:02:01.280
You do all the dirty and hard work

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:02.680
The internet cafe accounts, the club matters...

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:03.640
which one isn't managed by you?

00:02:05.480 --> 00:02:06.760
The way I see it, without you

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:07.879
they wouldn't have had the time

00:02:07.879 --> 00:02:09.199
to develop that hit game

00:02:09.599 --> 00:02:10.479
But look at things now

00:02:10.479 --> 00:02:11.800
They didn't bring you to the celebration party

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:13.039
You must feel bad about it, right?

00:02:14.680 --> 00:02:15.840
I... I don't

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:23.199
I understand how you feel

00:02:23.759 --> 00:02:26.199
When I worked on that domain site with Chen Fan

00:02:26.199 --> 00:02:27.599
when the site went live and we split the money

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:28.800
I didn't get a single cent

00:02:32.360 --> 00:02:33.560
Alright, stop looking at that

00:02:33.800 --> 00:02:34.039
Let's go

00:02:34.319 --> 00:02:35.560
I'll take you out for a drink and a chat

00:02:35.919 --> 00:02:36.599
I won't go

00:02:36.599 --> 00:02:37.800
I... I need to organize this

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:38.680
Let's just talk

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:39.919
See if we can come up with something

00:02:39.919 --> 00:02:41.199
that will really impress them

00:02:41.800 --> 00:02:42.439
Let's go, let's go

00:02:42.680 --> 00:02:43.159
Let's go

00:02:44.639 --> 00:02:45.080
Come on

00:02:46.960 --> 00:02:47.520
Wenjie

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:49.120
This thing here

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:50.599
is called a game easter egg

00:02:51.520 --> 00:02:53.479
It's like giving Liang Shichu and Chen Fan

00:02:53.479 --> 00:02:54.159
a little joke

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:57.599
I'm just afraid that if Brother Fan finds out

00:02:58.120 --> 00:02:59.319
he won't be happy

00:02:59.759 --> 00:03:01.400
I'll teach you step by step

00:03:01.400 --> 00:03:02.639
There's no way you'll be discovered

00:03:05.639 --> 00:03:06.159
Okay

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:07.840
It won't be discovered

00:03:08.479 --> 00:03:09.159
Let me tell you

00:03:09.159 --> 00:03:10.439
Maybe when they do find it

00:03:10.439 --> 00:03:11.599
they'll think your skills are rock solid

00:03:11.599 --> 00:03:12.639
and see you in a whole new light

00:03:14.800 --> 00:03:15.439
Bottoms up

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:23.879
In a bit, we'll go to the office

00:03:23.879 --> 00:03:25.680
You just take this thing, like I said

00:03:28.199 --> 00:03:28.639
Okay

00:03:28.639 --> 00:03:29.639
Come on, eat some more

00:03:34.919 --> 00:03:35.879
Chen Fan

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:38.560
Your good days are over

00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:44.759
Chen Fan and Brother Liang's celebration party

00:03:44.759 --> 00:03:46.000
should be right here

00:03:48.520 --> 00:03:49.840
Why don't I see the two of them?

00:03:50.520 --> 00:03:51.840
Seems this game isn't that popular after all

00:03:52.479 --> 00:03:54.080
We checked everything before the launch

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:55.000
How is this possible?

00:03:56.080 --> 00:03:56.759
Chen Fan!

00:03:57.400 --> 00:03:58.280
What is going on?

00:04:16.920 --> 00:04:18.639
What on earth happened here?

00:04:20.319 --> 00:04:21.480
I need to retrieve the disk quickly

00:04:21.639 --> 00:04:22.519
And wipe the traces

00:04:35.120 --> 00:04:36.360
What is he doing with the disk?

00:04:40.079 --> 00:04:40.800
Mr. Chen Fan.

00:04:41.319 --> 00:04:42.759
We are from the City Bureau's Cyber Police Division.

00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:44.839
In the game developed by you and Liang Shichu,

00:04:44.839 --> 00:04:45.560
it is suspected to contain

00:04:45.560 --> 00:04:47.399
hidden content that endangers social stability.

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:49.319
The game "Mecha Shanghai,"

00:04:49.319 --> 00:04:51.759
the copyright ownership and core program development

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:53.519
belong to you and Liang Shichu, correct?

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:54.639
Yes.

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:57.360
But our game absolutely has no illegal content.

00:04:57.680 --> 00:04:59.279
We checked the code repeatedly before launch.

00:04:59.279 --> 00:05:00.199
There can't be any problems.

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:03.439
This is impossible.

00:05:03.439 --> 00:05:05.120
Our game doesn't have that kind of thing.

00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:06.639
How could we possibly add something like that?

00:05:07.079 --> 00:05:08.000
This is what our technicians

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:08.839
just cracked and found.

00:05:08.839 --> 00:05:09.959
A hidden trigger mechanism.

00:05:10.279 --> 00:05:11.160
And you still claim you didn't know?

00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:12.839
These kinds of videos are everywhere online.

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:14.279
It's possible someone hacked the game

00:05:14.279 --> 00:05:14.920
and planted it in the backend.

00:05:14.920 --> 00:05:17.279
Theoretically, that possibility does exist.

00:05:17.399 --> 00:05:19.240
But your friend keeps emphasizing

00:05:19.759 --> 00:05:21.279
that your code is encrypted.

00:05:21.920 --> 00:05:23.120
According to him,

00:05:23.759 --> 00:05:24.839
unless it was an insider...

00:05:25.959 --> 00:05:26.759
An insider...

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:29.560
An insider would never do such a thing.

00:05:30.360 --> 00:05:31.279
Who could it be?

00:05:32.120 --> 00:05:33.000
This game of yours

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:34.480
has been spreading very rapidly recently.

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:35.519
The impact is extremely negative.

00:05:35.959 --> 00:05:37.160
As the lead creators,

00:05:37.160 --> 00:05:38.560
you must give an explanation.

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:40.279
Otherwise, no one is leaving.

00:05:41.079 --> 00:05:42.120
Think it over carefully.

00:05:44.800 --> 00:05:45.519
Let's go.

00:05:48.480 --> 00:05:49.360
Your cousin is here to see you.

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:50.759
Don't take too long.

00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:56.480
Cousin.

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:01.399
I know you don't want to see me right now.

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:03.480
But Ruochu asked me to come see you.

00:06:04.680 --> 00:06:05.360
How is she?

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:06.279
She's fine.

00:06:06.279 --> 00:06:07.800
The game has nothing to do with her, don't worry.

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:09.000
Please try to comfort her for me.

00:06:09.759 --> 00:06:11.319
Now I'm actually glad she dumped me.

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:13.920
I found a buddy with solid tech skills

00:06:14.279 --> 00:06:15.399
to check Luo Wenjie's computer.

00:06:15.399 --> 00:06:16.360
We found something.

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:17.600
Why did you investigate him?

00:06:22.680 --> 00:06:23.519
These are bank records.

00:06:24.079 --> 00:06:25.439
Transferred to him by people from Long Technology.

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:27.120
Right after your game's beta test.

00:06:27.959 --> 00:06:28.600
What does that mean?

00:06:28.879 --> 00:06:29.720
Keep reading.

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:32.120
There's another large transaction

00:06:32.199 --> 00:06:33.519
after the launch event ended.

00:06:33.519 --> 00:06:35.000
No, Wenjie would tell me if he needed money.

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:36.360
What does Long Corp have to do with it?

00:06:36.519 --> 00:06:37.120
Have you forgotten?

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:39.560
Previously, they were the ones who sent Liang Shichu

00:06:39.879 --> 00:06:41.000
to hack our domain network.

00:06:44.240 --> 00:06:45.439
Long Corp wants to make games too.

00:06:45.639 --> 00:06:46.439
We're in their way.

00:06:46.839 --> 00:06:47.199
Right?

00:06:47.399 --> 00:06:48.519
I think it's not just the game.

00:06:49.079 --> 00:06:50.360
Maybe the antivirus software you made before

00:06:50.360 --> 00:06:51.920
already blocked their path to profit.

00:06:53.519 --> 00:06:56.600
You mean to say Wenjie was bought off by Long Corp,

00:06:56.720 --> 00:06:58.759
and they made him add these things to the game

00:06:58.759 --> 00:07:00.040
to frame me and Liang?

00:07:00.240 --> 00:07:01.360
Chen Fan, you have to understand,

00:07:01.920 --> 00:07:03.199
he's not like us.

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:04.439
He's always been a businessman.

00:07:04.439 --> 00:07:05.319
He's always looked towards money.

00:07:05.319 --> 00:07:06.160
Impossible.

00:07:06.519 --> 00:07:07.360
I know him.

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:08.120
He's not that kind of person.

00:07:08.120 --> 00:07:08.839
The police said

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:11.639
they found no traces of forgery in this transaction.

00:07:15.279 --> 00:07:16.360
The police know?

00:07:17.480 --> 00:07:18.279
Did you tell them?

00:07:19.519 --> 00:07:21.000
You couldn't hide this even if you wanted to.

00:07:21.399 --> 00:07:22.519
And the police also said

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:24.759
they found other things on him as well.

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:31.639
Alright, time is just about up.

00:07:31.639 --> 00:07:32.240
I have to go.

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:33.680
Think it over again,

00:07:34.079 --> 00:07:35.560
about whether there was anything off about him.

00:07:50.920 --> 00:07:51.480
Chen Fan

00:07:51.879 --> 00:07:52.639
You can go now.

00:07:54.120 --> 00:07:54.680
Go.

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:56.600
It's all right now.

00:07:57.160 --> 00:07:58.160
Then what about Brother Liang?

00:07:58.160 --> 00:07:59.519
He still needs to cooperate with the investigation.

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:00.920
Why?

00:08:01.040 --> 00:08:02.920
Liang Shichu has explained everything to us clearly.

00:08:03.399 --> 00:08:06.439
He said the game's core program, from development to maintenance,

00:08:06.759 --> 00:08:08.040
was all done by him alone.

00:08:08.199 --> 00:08:09.759
All the technical parameter details

00:08:09.920 --> 00:08:11.120
are known only to him.

00:08:11.639 --> 00:08:12.160
And you,

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:14.360
didn't touch any technical aspects throughout the process.

00:08:14.439 --> 00:08:16.439
You only participated in the initial planning

00:08:16.639 --> 00:08:17.360
and later operations.

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:20.160
Brother Liang is trying to take the blame for everyone.

00:08:20.839 --> 00:08:22.720
So you can leave for now.

00:08:22.839 --> 00:08:23.439
Officer,

00:08:23.639 --> 00:08:25.040
regarding this... this project...

00:08:25.040 --> 00:08:26.279
I... I... I also participated.

00:08:26.600 --> 00:08:27.680
You're all still college students, right?

00:08:28.639 --> 00:08:30.160
Instead of wasting time on loyalty here,

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:31.360
you should hurry back.

00:08:31.720 --> 00:08:33.039
If there really are any suspicious points,

00:08:33.559 --> 00:08:34.840
only you yourselves know best.

00:08:37.399 --> 00:08:38.080
I understand.

00:08:38.600 --> 00:08:39.679
Thank you, Officer.

00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:46.519
Chen Fan, oh Chen Fan.

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:48.919
You were a CEO in your past life, after all.

00:08:49.159 --> 00:08:50.720
How did you still fall for this?

00:08:51.320 --> 00:08:52.879
Causing Brother Liang to shoulder everything

00:08:53.120 --> 00:08:53.919
and get detained.

00:08:56.440 --> 00:08:56.919
Brother Fan.

00:08:58.600 --> 00:08:59.080
Guo Shuai.

00:09:02.519 --> 00:09:04.200
Alright, stop looking at me like that.

00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:05.759
It's no big deal.

00:09:09.159 --> 00:09:10.120
Did you bring a power bank?

00:09:10.759 --> 00:09:11.440
Power what?

00:09:13.320 --> 00:09:13.799
I forgot.

00:09:14.240 --> 00:09:15.519
I'll just change the battery when I get back.

00:09:18.440 --> 00:09:19.000
Brother Fan.

00:09:19.159 --> 00:09:20.919
What exactly happened with your website?

00:09:21.200 --> 00:09:22.559
Yesterday it was popular all over the internet,

00:09:22.559 --> 00:09:23.919
and all the young people were playing it.

00:09:23.919 --> 00:09:25.919
But today it was suddenly cut off,

00:09:26.159 --> 00:09:26.960
and completely banned.

00:09:27.399 --> 00:09:28.519
I want to know too.

00:09:29.200 --> 00:09:30.000
Brother Fan.

00:09:30.399 --> 00:09:32.840
Actually, ever since I came to Yunhai City,

00:09:32.840 --> 00:09:33.960
I've really envied you.

00:09:34.559 --> 00:09:36.080
Opening internet cafes, opening clubs.

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:36.960
I think you're amazing.

00:09:36.960 --> 00:09:38.159
I'm really happy for you.

00:09:38.360 --> 00:09:41.759
But you end up either reported or inspected.

00:09:41.919 --> 00:09:43.080
You're just too unlucky.

00:09:44.480 --> 00:09:46.080
Maybe this is fate.

00:09:46.360 --> 00:09:46.840
Brother Fan.

00:09:47.080 --> 00:09:48.639
You can't talk about fate and stuff.

00:09:49.399 --> 00:09:51.080
I'm still waiting to be your sidekick.

00:09:55.519 --> 00:09:57.240
Blame me for being a bad father.

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:58.720
I helped you avoid jail time,

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:00.320
but couldn't help you avoid this injury.

00:10:01.039 --> 00:10:02.200
Screw you.

00:10:04.759 --> 00:10:05.519
Brother Fan.

00:10:06.159 --> 00:10:09.039
Actually, ever since my leg accident,

00:10:09.039 --> 00:10:10.440
every day I either keep my parents company

00:10:10.759 --> 00:10:11.720
or keep Lingling company.

00:10:11.879 --> 00:10:13.080
I'm really quite happy.

00:10:13.639 --> 00:10:16.360
So I'm really grateful to you.

00:10:19.960 --> 00:10:22.600
Brother Fan, living a steady life is what's real.

00:10:28.039 --> 00:10:28.639
You kid.

00:10:29.480 --> 00:10:30.879
You've really seen the light now.

00:10:31.639 --> 00:10:32.519
I'm relieved too.

00:10:37.799 --> 00:10:39.639
To see Chen Fan publicly humiliated

00:10:39.919 --> 00:10:41.720
is truly a delightful thing.

00:10:41.960 --> 00:10:43.919
The disk you brought back is also very useful.

00:10:43.919 --> 00:10:45.840
Besides the code for Mecha Shanghai Bund,

00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:47.639
there are also prototypes for a few software programs.

00:10:48.440 --> 00:10:49.639
We'll take them, modify them a bit,

00:10:49.759 --> 00:10:50.639
and launch them directly to the market.

00:10:50.879 --> 00:10:52.240
Saves us from developing from scratch.

00:10:53.120 --> 00:10:54.960
As long as it's useful, as long as it's useful.

00:10:56.559 --> 00:10:58.440
You look like someone who can hustle.

00:10:59.039 --> 00:11:01.360
Unlike those useless cowards.

00:11:01.840 --> 00:11:03.399
I happen to have a bigger project.

00:11:03.840 --> 00:11:05.519
Do you dare to do it with me?

00:11:07.720 --> 00:11:10.440
Mr. Liu, as long as it's something you order,

00:11:10.679 --> 00:11:11.759
I will definitely go all out.

00:11:12.279 --> 00:11:14.200
It's a project linked to the company's overseas business.

00:11:14.480 --> 00:11:15.960
The risk is a bit high,

00:11:15.960 --> 00:11:18.759
but once it's done, you'll rise to the top.

00:11:19.720 --> 00:11:21.559
Mr. Liu, as long as you're willing to guide me,

00:11:22.320 --> 00:11:23.360
there's nothing I wouldn't dare do.

00:11:23.519 --> 00:11:24.279
That's good.

00:11:27.080 --> 00:11:28.519
The project Manager Liu mentioned

00:11:28.879 --> 00:11:30.320
must be organ trafficking.

00:11:31.840 --> 00:11:32.279
No.

00:11:32.879 --> 00:11:34.039
I have to stop all this.